  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"maincontent\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eMore of us than ever before are choosing to travel with our dogs. We’d love to hear about your favourite pet-friendly holiday in the UK or Europe. Whether it’s a hotel that goes out of its way to pamper your pooch, a beach that’s perfect for walkies with somewhere dog-friendly to stay nearby, or a road trip where your four-legged friend came along for the ride, we’d love to hear your recommendations.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe best tip of the week, chosen by \u003ca href=\"https://www.lonelyplanet.com/\" data-link-name=\"in body link\"\u003eTom Hall of Lonely Planet\u003c/a\u003e, will \u003cstrong\u003ewin a £200 voucher to stay at a \u003ca href=\"https://www.coolstays.com/\" data-link-name=\"in body link\"\u003eCoolstays\u003c/a\u003e property\u003c/strong\u003e – the company has more than 3,000 worldwide. The best tips will appear in the Guardian Travel section and website.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eIf you have a relevant photo, do send it in –\u003cstrong\u003e but it’s your words that will be judged\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003efor the competition\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eKeep your tip to about 100 words\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eWe’re sorry, but for legal reasons \u003cstrong\u003eyou must be a UK resident \u003c/strong\u003eto enter this competition.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eThe competition closes on 26 May at 10am BST\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/travel/series/readers-travel-tips\" data-link-name=\"in body link\"\u003eHave a look at our past winners and other tips\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/travel/2013/jun/28/been-there-readers-tips-competition-terms-and-conditions\" data-link-name=\"in body link\"\u003eRead the terms and conditions here\u003c/a\